name: Gwt-blocks
body:
### Welcome to GWT-Blocks
This respository aims to help for the development of GWT projects.  
Add to your projects 3 new widgets: loading box, prettypopup, togglebutton.  
Add new events for togglebutton: toggleEvent and hasToggleEvent.  
Manages your URL places with PlaceManager.
Better abstraction from presenter-display model.

### Use in projects
This tool is used on the follow projects:  
[@Map4RDF](http://oeg-upm.github.io/map4rdf/)

### Understand this project  
For understand this project you need to know:  
[GWT](http://www.gwtproject.org/)  
[GWT Inject](https://code.google.com/archive/p/google-gin/)  
[GWT Dispatch](https://github.com/randombits-org/gwt-dispatch)  
[GWT Presenter](https://code.google.com/archive/p/gwt-presenter/)   
[Guice servlet](https://github.com/google/guice/wiki/Servlets)  


### Authors and Contributors
[@alexdeleon](https://github.com/alexdeleon) and [@Fransiro](https://github.com/Fransiro/)

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with gwt-blocks? Check out our [documentation](https://github.com/oeg-upm/gwt-blocks/blob/master/README.MD) or [contact support](mailto:ocorcho@fi.upm.es) and weâ€™ll help you sort it out.
